snippet.textDisplay:
بِسۡمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ
In the name of ALLAH, the Entirely Merciful, the Especially Merciful.
قُلۡ هُوَٱللَّهُ أَحَدٌ(1)
Say "He is ALLAH, [Who is] one, (1)
ٱللَّهُ ٱلصَّمَدُ(2)
ALLAH,the Enternal Refuge(2)
لَمۡ يَلِدۡوَلَمۡ يُولَدۡ(3)
He neither begets nor he is born (3)
وَلَمۡ يَكُن لَّهُۥكُفُوًاأَحَدُۢ(4)
Nor is there to him any equivalent" (4)
❤
